== 各国 ==

=== {{阿尔巴尼亚}} ===
[[阿尔巴尼亚|阿尔巴尼亚]]共产主义罪行研究所（ICC）提议禁止播放共产主义时期的电影，引发了公众的负面反应。<ref name="Proposed Ban on Albanian Communist Films Sparks Backlash">{{Citation|title=Proposed Ban on Albanian Communist Films Sparks Backlash|url=https://balkaninsight.com/2017/03/16/initiative-to-ban-albanian-communist-movies-couse-backlash-03-15-2017|publisher=Balkan Insight|last=Fatjona Mejdini|date=2017-03-16|access-date=2017-04-01|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307212055/https://balkaninsight.com/2017/03/16/initiative-to-ban-albanian-communist-movies-couse-backlash-03-15-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== {{保加利亚}} ===
[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]于2016年11月24日对拟议法律进行一读表决，规定公开展示共产主义标志为非法。这项法律要求将共产主义政权时期制作的美化前共产党及其领导人的标志和物品从公共场所移除。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Parliament Passes Amendments to Act Declaring the Criminal Nature of the Communist Regime in Bulgaria|url=http://www.bta.bg/en/c/DF/id/1466614|accessdate=2018-10-07|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707092539/http://www.bta.bg/en/c/DF/id/1466614|archivedate=2018-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=New protests for the removal of the statue of the Soviet Army in Sofia|url=https://www.euscoop.com/en/2017/9/7/protests-for-removal-of-soviet-monument|accessdate=2018-10-07|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707042637/https://www.euscoop.com/en/2017/9/7/protests-for-removal-of-soviet-monument|archivedate=2018-07-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Bulgaria bans public display of communist symbols|url=https://www.calvertjournal.com/articles/show/7304/bulgaria-bans-public-display-of-communist-symbols|accessdate=2018-10-07|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716020855/https://www.calvertjournal.com/articles/show/7304/bulgaria-bans-public-display-of-communist-symbols|archivedate=2019-07-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，该提案未付诸二读，也未经过保加利亚总统签署或在保加利亚国家公报上公布，因此未成为法律。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Народно събрание на Република България - Законопроекти|url=https://parliament.bg/bg/bills/ID/15831|accessdate=2019-10-16|work=parliament.bg|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016163812/http://parliament.bg/bg/bills/ID/15831|archivedate=2019-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== {{克罗地亚}} ===
