=== {{乌克兰}} ===
2015年4月，[[乌克兰最高拉达|最高拉达]]通过了一部禁止共产党和纳粹标志的法律。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Goodbye, Lenin: Ukraine moves to ban communist symbols|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-32267075|accessdate=2019-12-18|author=Shevchenko|date=2015-04-14|first=Vitaly|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307200441/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-32267075|archivedate=2016-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>早在2012年，乌克兰西部的[[利沃夫|利沃夫市]]就禁止公开显示共产主义符号。<ref name="runei" />2015年12月17日，所有共产党在乌克兰均被正式禁止。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ukraine bans Communist party for 'promoting separatism'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/dec/17/ukraine-bans-communist-party-separatism|accessdate=2019-12-18|date=2015-12-17|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225234337/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/dec/17/ukraine-bans-communist-party-separatism|archivedate=2019-12-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌唱或演奏[[苏联|苏联]]前国歌或其他任何加盟共和國前国歌可判处最高五年徒刑。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ukraine bans Soviet symbols and criminalises sympathy for communism|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/may/21/ukraine-bans-soviet-symbols-criminalises-sympathy-for-communism|accessdate=2019-12-18|author=Luhn|date=2015-05-21|first=Alec|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222123954/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/may/21/ukraine-bans-soviet-symbols-criminalises-sympathy-for-communism|archivedate=2019-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年7月，宪法法院维持了该法律，将共产主义等同于纳粹主义。<ref>{{Cite web|title=RFE/RL: Ukraine's Constitutional Court upholds law equating communism to Nazism|url=https://www.kyivpost.com/ukraine-politics/rfe-rl-ukraines-constitutional-court-upholds-law-equating-communism-to-nazism.html|accessdate=2019-12-18|date=2019-07-17|publisher=[[Kyiv_Post|Kyiv Post]]|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522162827/https://www.kyivpost.com/ukraine-politics/rfe-rl-ukraines-constitutional-court-upholds-law-equating-communism-to-nazism.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ukraine's Constitutional Court Upholds Law Equating Communism To Nazism|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/ukraine-s-constitutional-court-upholds-law-equating-communism-to-nazism/30060259.html|accessdate=2020-05-04|work=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122083436/https://www.rferl.org/a/ukraine-s-constitutional-court-upholds-law-equating-communism-to-nazism/30060259.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

